product.title: Pepper and Salt Cat Sharing Love Hoodie
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • This hoodie is purr-fectly adorable!

    This Pepper and Salt Cat Sharing Love Hoodie is perfect for any cat-lover looking to spread some feline affection! It's made with ultra-soft fabric and features the cutest cat duo snuggled up in a loving embrace - aww, how heart warming! So, bundle up in the purrfect pick-me-up and love on!

    Choose between 11 different colors, suitable for both men and women. We always recommend choosing 1 size up giving you the oversized hoodie look.

    Asian Size (inches)
    Asian Metrics S M L XL 2XL 3XL
    Bust 37 38 40 41 43 44
    Length 26 27 28 29 30 31
    Asian Size (cm)
    Asian Metrics S M L XL 2XL 3XL
    Bust 96 98 102 106 110 114
    Length 66 69 72 75 78 80



    Perfect for your everyday look!

    Show off your love for pandas with this hoodie. Made from premium quality polyester and cotton, this hoodie is like no other and feels soft and smooth on the skin. A super comfortable overlay for everyday wear.

    Available in five different sizes for all to wear, measurements are shown below. 


    Size (inches) S M L XL XXL
    Bust 41 43 44 46 48
    Length 23 24 25 26 27
    Sleeve 20 20 20 21 21
               
    Size (cm) S M L XL XXL
    Bust 106 110 114 118 122
    Length 60 62 64 66 68
    Sleeve 50 51 52 53 54


    Features

    😍 Made from 70% premium polyester and 30% pure cotton
    😍 Promotes warmth, comfort, and durability
    😍 Two Red Pandas in Love printed on the front only

    Measurements may be off by 1-5cm for rounding up to a whole number.

    If you are interested in more kawaii plushies like this, please check out our website www.kawaiies.com.

  • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

     Dry cleaning

     

  • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, Spain, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.

    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: Est 5-30 Business days
